<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>: (و (} الهُوَّةُ،<span class="c5"> كقُوَّةٍ:</span> مَا انْهَبَطَ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>